<p itemprop="description">An IT service manager is responsible for the end-to-end delivery of IT services to business users. They ensure services meet agreed service levels, manage service relationships, and drive continuous service improvement.</p>

<section class="role-details">
    <h2>Typical responsibilities</h2>
    <ul>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Manage end-to-end IT service delivery and performance</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Ensure services meet agreed service level agreements</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Build and maintain relationships with business stakeholders</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Coordinate service improvement initiatives and projects</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Manage service budgets and financial performance</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Lead service reviews and governance activities</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Support service transition and change activities</li>
    </ul>
</section>

